# The client needs no env vars in dev — this is the only knob it reads.

# The API base URL, baked in at build time (it's a VITE_ var). When unset,
# dev builds fall back to the local server on http://localhost:3001, and
# production builds fail loudly at startup — a silent localhost fallback in
# prod would strand every real call. Vercel sets it to
# https://api.chaverola.com for Production and Preview. See src/lib/api.ts.
#VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:3001
